            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:SWinxy&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SWinxy&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Mahmoud_Khalil_NYC_detention_protest_050.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Wikimedia Commons.&lt;/a&gt; Licensed under the &lt;a href=&quot;https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/deed.en&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International license&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
