            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wvxu.org/politics/2025-03-13/analysis-save-act-disenfranchise-women-military-voters&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NPR - 91.7 WVXU News) What the SAVE Act Does, and how it Could Disenfranchise Millions of Voters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.congress.gov/bill/119th-congress/house-bill/22&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Congress.gov) H.R. 22 - SAVE Act&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
