        &lt;p&gt;This as a massive, nationwide call, so it&#39;s not targeted to specific events or activities in your area, but the hosts do try to answer questions submitted in advance or during the call. They can&#39;t get to all of them, but they do a good job of cutting through the noise and encouraging real actions you can take.&lt;/p&gt;
